{"story":{"group_1":[{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3503_mirrors_memory.ExportJson","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104400,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story17","chara":[{"id":104400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-1"}],"nameNarration":"Mikoto","narration":"\"The cycle of destruction that surrounds mankind,@unchanging over thousands and thousands of years...\"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":104400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-2"}],"narration":"\"With both malice and good will alike,@humans pursue harm and destruction.\""},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-3"}],"narration":"\"You've already seen plenty of examples@of humans unconsciously seeking death,@so what kind of destruction would you like to see next?\""},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104400,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-4"}],"narration":"\"Oh yeah, it might be a good idea to show you@that no matter how hard they try,@humans are beyond saving.\""},{"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":104400}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter11/103203_worldmap.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"bgFront"}],"narration":"\"So, what the mirror will now reflect is how@[textRed:people will destroy each other even if they find salvation].\"","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-5"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":101200,"motion":300,"pos":2,"posX":60},{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":100800,"motion":0,"pos":0,"posX":-60}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter11/103203_india_map.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"bgFront"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":101200,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-6"}],"nameRight":"Karin","textRight":"Alina-senpai, I understand.@I don't want to see any more of this.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":100800,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-7"}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"No problema."},{"chara":[{"id":100800,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-8"}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"What you're about to see isn't scary, so you should@be able to watch with peace of mind."},{"chara":[{"id":101200,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-9"}],"nameRight":"Karin","textRight":"It still looks peaceful, but I was@fooled by that before..."},{"chara":[{"id":101200,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-10"},{"id":100800,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Karin","textRight":"There... Just for believing in God,@that woman is about to be killed."},{"chara":[{"id":101200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-11"}],"nameRight":"Karin","textRight":"Her mom is trying to kill her...and her fianc√© too..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":101200,"motion":400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-12"}],"nameRight":"Karin","textRight":"Oh, what's that...? It looks like she's okay..."},{"chara":[{"id":100800,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-13"}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"Yes, she's just fine."},{"chara":[{"id":100800,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-14"}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"Even when they try to burn her at the stake,@she manages to fuggire."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter11/103203_syria_puella.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"bgFront"},{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter11/103203_india_map.jpg","visible":"hide"}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"id":100800,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-15"}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"Even when they try to feed her to the animales,@she survives."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":101200,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-16"}],"nameRight":"Karin","textRight":"In fact, the animals are trying to protect her."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":101200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-17"}],"nameRight":"Karin","textRight":"It's a series of miracles!"},{"chara":[{"id":100800,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-18"}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"That's why everyone came to her, out of rispetto."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":101200,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-19"}],"nameRight":"Karin","textRight":"Even after they all tried to kill her, she's@teaching them how to love each other."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":101200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-20"}],"nameRight":"Karin","textRight":"If everyone listen's to her story,@they'll all become kinder!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"flashEffect":"flashRed2","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter11/103203_syria_puella.jpg","visible":"hide"}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"id":100800,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-21"}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"But such instruction is ultimately meaningless.@Sooner or later, humans turn to conflict."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":101200,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-22"}],"nameRight":"Karin","textRight":"This is weird... Everyone should@be afraid of fighting... So why...?"},{"chara":[{"id":101200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-23"}],"nameRight":"Karin","textRight":"The importance of love was passed down@to the next generation, and still..."},{"chara":[{"id":100800,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-24"}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"So long as the concetto of \"us\" and them\" exists,"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp3.json","id":100800,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-25"}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"humans cannot erase their will to segregare,@and so the war continues."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter11/103203_worldmap.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"bgFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"rollIn"},{"nameNarration":"Mikoto","narration":"\"And you know...@[textRed:Humans even deny their very roots].\"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"rollOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-26"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":101200,"motion":0,"pos":2,"posX":60},{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":100800,"motion":0,"pos":0,"posX":-60}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter11/103203_piedmont_map.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"bgFront"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":104400,"motion":100,"pos":0,"posX":-60,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-27"}],"nameLeft":"Mikoto","textLeft":"Look, see there? There's a brave woman fighting."},{"chara":[{"id":101200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-28"}],"nameRight":"Karin","textRight":"Yeah..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter11/103203_india_puella.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"bgFront"},{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter11/103203_piedmont_map.jpg","visible":"hide"}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"id":104400,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-29"}],"nameLeft":"Mikoto","textLeft":"She was intelligent, powerful, and just@better than her brothers."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-30"}],"nameLeft":"Mikoto","textLeft":"That's why she became the king, but she@was looked down on just for being a woman."},{"chara":[{"id":101200,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-31"}],"nameRight":"Karin","textRight":"I think that's still something that happens today."},{"chara":[{"id":101200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-32"}],"nameRight":"Karin","textRight":"I heard that it used to be a lot worse..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104400,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-33"}],"nameLeft":"Mikoto","textLeft":"Yes, from the very beginning, it's been human@nature to reject others over gender."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":100800,"motion":200,"pos":0,"posX":-60,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-34"}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"For humans...no, for all living things,@gender is a necessary distinzione."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104400,"motion":1,"pos":0,"posX":-60,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-35"}],"nameLeft":"Mikoto","textLeft":"And yet, this woman dressed and acted like a man."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":100800,"motion":300,"pos":0,"posX":-60,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-36"}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"So it was that the conflict@of gender became a trigger,"},{"chara":[{"id":100800,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-37"}],"nameLeft":"Alina","textLeft":"and she was killed in the conflitto."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"flashEffect":"flashRed2","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter11/103203_india_puella.jpg","visible":"hide"}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":104400,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":104400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-38"}],"nameNarration":"Mikoto","narration":"\"Perhaps people unconsciously seek out conflict,@and that leads to destruction.\"","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":104400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-39"}],"narration":"\"But it doesn't matter if@you're looking for conflict or not,\""},{"chara":[{"id":104400,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-40"}],"narration":"\"because from the moment we are born, we reject@based on the very foundation of life, gender.\""},{"chara":[{"id":104400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-41"}],"narration":"\"We are destroyed by the very@system which gives birth to us.\""},{"chara":[{"id":104400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-4-42"}],"narration":"\"If you want more, I can show you.@I have so many more examples,@too many to even list.\""},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
